#. <section class="sutta" id="mn132"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "mn132:0.1"
msgid "Majjhima Nikāya 132"
msgstr "Middle Discourses 132"

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "mn132:0.2"
msgid "Ānandabhaddekarattasutta"
msgstr "Ānanda and One Fine Night"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="nya" id="nya1"></a>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pi" id="pts-vp-pi3.190"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "mn132:1.1"
msgid "Evaṃ me sutaṃ—​"
msgstr "So I have heard."

msgctxt "mn132:1.2"
msgid ""
"ekaṃ samayaṃ bhagavā sāvatthiyaṃ viharati jetavane anāthapiṇḍikassa ārāme."
msgstr ""
"At one time the Buddha was staying near Sāvatthī in Jeta’s Grove, "
"Anāthapiṇḍika’s monastery."

#. <a class="nya" id="nya2"></a>
msgctxt "mn132:2.1"
msgid ""
"Tena kho pana samayena āyasmā ānando upaṭṭhānasālāyaṃ bhikkhūnaṃ dhammiyā "
"kathāya sandasseti samādapeti samuttejeti sampahaṃseti, bhaddekarattassa "
"uddesañca vibhaṅgañca bhāsati."
msgstr ""
"Now at that time Venerable Ānanda was educating, encouraging, firing up, and "
"inspiring the mendicants in the assembly hall with a Dhamma talk on the "
"topic of the recitation passage and analysis of One Fine Night."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "mn132:2.2"
msgid ""
"Atha kho bhagavā sāyanhasamayaṃ paṭisallānā vuṭṭhito yenupaṭṭhānasālā "
"tenupasaṅkami; upasaṅkamitvā paññatte āsane nisīdi."
msgstr ""
"Then in the late afternoon, the Buddha came out of retreat, went to the "
"assembly hall, where he sat on the seat spread out,"

msgctxt "mn132:2.3"
msgid "Nisajja kho bhagavā bhikkhū āmantesi:"
msgstr "and addressed the mendicants:"

msgctxt "mn132:2.4"
msgid ""
"“ko nu kho, bhikkhave, upaṭṭhānasālāyaṃ bhikkhūnaṃ dhammiyā kathāya "
"sandassesi samādapesi samuttejesi sampahaṃsesi, bhaddekarattassa uddesañca "
"vibhaṅgañca abhāsī”ti?"
msgstr ""
"“Who was inspiring the mendicants with a talk on the recitation passage and "
"analysis of One Fine Night?”"

msgctxt "mn132:2.5"
msgid ""
"“Āyasmā, bhante, ānando upaṭṭhānasālāyaṃ bhikkhūnaṃ dhammiyā kathāya "
"sandassesi samādapesi samuttejesi sampahaṃsesi, bhaddekarattassa uddesañca "
"vibhaṅgañca abhāsī”ti."
msgstr "“It was Venerable Ānanda, sir.”"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc3"></a>
msgctxt "mn132:2.6"
msgid "Atha kho bhagavā āyasmantaṃ ānandaṃ āmantesi:"
msgstr "Then the Buddha said to Venerable Ānanda:"

msgctxt "mn132:2.7"
msgid ""
"“yathā kathaṃ pana tvaṃ, ānanda, bhikkhūnaṃ dhammiyā kathāya sandassesi "
"samādapesi samuttejesi sampahaṃsesi, bhaddekarattassa uddesañca vibhaṅgañca "
"abhāsī”ti?"
msgstr ""
"“But in what way were you inspiring the mendicants with a talk on the "
"recitation passage and analysis of One Fine Night?”"

#. <a class="nya" id="nya3"></a>
msgctxt "mn132:3.1"
msgid ""
"“Evaṃ kho ahaṃ, bhante, bhikkhūnaṃ dhammiyā kathāya sandassesiṃ samādapesiṃ "
"samuttejesiṃ sampahaṃsesiṃ, bhaddekarattassa uddesañca vibhaṅgañca abhāsiṃ—"
msgstr ""
"“I was doing so in this way, sir,” replied Ānanda. (And he went on to repeat "
"the verses and analysis as in the previous discourse, MN 131.)"

#. </p><blockquote class="gatha"><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc4"></a>
msgctxt "mn132:3.2"
msgid "Atītaṃ nānvāgameyya,"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "mn132:3.3"
msgid "nappaṭikaṅkhe anāgataṃ;"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "mn132:3.4"
msgid "Yadatītaṃ pahīnaṃ taṃ,"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "mn132:3.5"
msgid "appattañca anāgataṃ."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc5"></a>
msgctxt "mn132:3.6"
msgid "Paccuppannañca yo dhammaṃ,"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "mn132:3.7"
msgid "tattha tattha vipassati;"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "mn132:3.8"
msgid "Asaṃhīraṃ asaṅkuppaṃ,"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "mn132:3.9"
msgid "taṃ vidvā manubrūhaye."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc6"></a>
msgctxt "mn132:3.10"
msgid "Ajjeva kiccamātappaṃ,"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "mn132:3.11"
msgid "ko jaññā maraṇaṃ suve;"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "mn132:3.12"
msgid "Na hi no saṅgaraṃ tena,"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "mn132:3.13"
msgid "mahāsenena maccunā."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc7"></a>
msgctxt "mn132:3.14"
msgid "Evaṃvihāriṃ ātāpiṃ,"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "mn132:3.15"
msgid "ahorattamatanditaṃ;"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "mn132:3.16"
msgid "Taṃ ve bhaddekarattoti,"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "mn132:3.17"
msgid "santo ācikkhate muni."
msgstr ""

#. </p></blockquote><p>
#. <a class="nya" id="nya4"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc8"></a>
msgctxt "mn132:4.1"
msgid "‘Kathañca, āvuso, atītaṃ anvāgameti?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn132:4.2"
msgid ""
"Evaṃrūpo ahosiṃ atītamaddhānanti tattha nandiṃ samanvāneti, evaṃvedano "
"ahosiṃ atītamaddhānanti tattha nandiṃ samanvāneti, evaṃsañño ahosiṃ "
"atītamaddhānanti tattha nandiṃ samanvāneti, evaṃsaṅkhāro ahosiṃ "
"atītamaddhānanti tattha nandiṃ samanvāneti, evaṃviññāṇo ahosiṃ "
"atītamaddhānanti tattha nandiṃ samanvāneti—"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn132:4.3"
msgid "evaṃ kho, āvuso, atītaṃ anvāgameti."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="nya" id="nya5"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc9"></a>
msgctxt "mn132:5.1"
msgid "Kathañca, āvuso, atītaṃ nānvāgameti?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn132:5.2"
msgid ""
"Evaṃrūpo ahosiṃ atītamaddhānanti tattha nandiṃ na samanvāneti, evaṃvedano "
"ahosiṃ atītamaddhānanti tattha nandiṃ na samanvāneti, evaṃsañño ahosiṃ "
"atītamaddhānanti tattha nandiṃ na samanvāneti, evaṃsaṅkhāro ahosiṃ "
"atītamaddhānanti tattha nandiṃ na samanvāneti, evaṃviññāṇo ahosiṃ "
"atītamaddhānanti tattha nandiṃ na samanvāneti—"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn132:5.3"
msgid "evaṃ kho, āvuso, atītaṃ nānvāgameti."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="nya" id="nya6"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc10"></a>
msgctxt "mn132:6.1"
msgid "Kathañca, āvuso, anāgataṃ paṭikaṅkhati?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn132:6.2"
msgid ""
"Evaṃrūpo siyaṃ anāgatamaddhānanti tattha nandiṃ samanvāneti, evaṃvedano "
"siyaṃ … pe …"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn132:6.3"
msgid "evaṃsañño siyaṃ …"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn132:6.4"
msgid "evaṃsaṅkhāro siyaṃ …"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn132:6.5"
msgid "evaṃviññāṇo siyaṃ anāgatamaddhānanti tattha nandiṃ samanvāneti—"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn132:6.6"
msgid "evaṃ kho, āvuso, anāgataṃ paṭikaṅkhati."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="nya" id="nya7"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc11"></a>
msgctxt "mn132:7.1"
msgid "Kathañca, āvuso, anāgataṃ nappaṭikaṅkhati?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn132:7.2"
msgid ""
"Evaṃrūpo siyaṃ anāgatamaddhānanti tattha nandiṃ na samanvāneti, evaṃvedano "
"siyaṃ … pe …"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn132:7.3"
msgid "evaṃsañño siyaṃ …"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn132:7.4"
msgid "evaṃsaṅkhāro siyaṃ …"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn132:7.5"
msgid "evaṃviññāṇo siyaṃ anāgatamaddhānanti tattha nandiṃ na samanvāneti—"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn132:7.6"
msgid "evaṃ kho, āvuso, anāgataṃ nappaṭikaṅkhati."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="nya" id="nya8"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc12"></a>
msgctxt "mn132:8.1"
msgid "Kathañca, āvuso, paccuppannesu dhammesu saṃhīrati?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn132:8.2"
msgid ""
"Idha, āvuso, assutavā puthujjano ariyānaṃ adassāvī ariyadhammassa akovido "
"ariyadhamme avinīto sappurisānaṃ adassāvī sappurisadhammassa akovido "
"sappurisadhamme avinīto "
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn132:8.3"
msgid ""
"rūpaṃ attato samanupassati, rūpavantaṃ vā attānaṃ, attani vā rūpaṃ, rūpasmiṃ "
"vā attānaṃ;"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn132:8.4"
msgid "vedanaṃ …"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn132:8.5"
msgid "saññaṃ …"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn132:8.6"
msgid "saṅkhāre …"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn132:8.7"
msgid ""
"viññāṇaṃ attato samanupassati, viññāṇavantaṃ vā attānaṃ, attani vā viññāṇaṃ, "
"viññāṇasmiṃ vā attānaṃ—"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn132:8.8"
msgid "evaṃ kho, āvuso, paccuppannesu dhammesu saṃhīrati."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="nya" id="nya9"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc13"></a>
msgctxt "mn132:9.1"
msgid "Kathañca, āvuso, paccuppannesu dhammesu na saṃhīrati?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn132:9.2"
msgid ""
"Idha, āvuso, sutavā ariyasāvako ariyānaṃ dassāvī ariyadhammassa kovido "
"ariyadhamme suvinīto sappurisānaṃ dassāvī sappurisadhammassa kovido "
"sappurisadhamme suvinīto "
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn132:9.3"
msgid ""
"na rūpaṃ attato samanupassati, na rūpavantaṃ vā attānaṃ, na attani vā rūpaṃ, "
"na rūpasmiṃ vā attānaṃ;"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn132:9.4"
msgid "na vedanaṃ …"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn132:9.5"
msgid "na saññaṃ …"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn132:9.6"
msgid "na saṅkhāre …"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn132:9.7"
msgid ""
"na viññāṇaṃ attato samanupassati, na viññāṇavantaṃ vā attānaṃ, na attani vā "
"viññāṇaṃ, na viññāṇasmiṃ vā attānaṃ—"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn132:9.8"
msgid "evaṃ kho, āvuso, paccuppannesu dhammesu na saṃhīrati."
msgstr ""

#. </p><blockquote class="gatha"><p>
#. <a class="nya" id="nya10"></a>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pi" id="pts-vp-pi3.191"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc14"></a>
