msgid "Atītaṃ nānvāgameyya,"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "mn132:10.2"
msgid "nappaṭikaṅkhe anāgataṃ;"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "mn132:10.3"
msgid "Yadatītaṃ pahīnaṃ taṃ,"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "mn132:10.4"
msgid "appattañca anāgataṃ."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc15"></a>
msgctxt "mn132:10.5"
msgid "Paccuppannañca yo dhammaṃ,"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "mn132:10.6"
msgid "tattha tattha vipassati;"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "mn132:10.7"
msgid "Asaṃhīraṃ asaṅkuppaṃ,"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "mn132:10.8"
msgid "taṃ vidvā manubrūhaye."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc16"></a>
msgctxt "mn132:10.9"
msgid "Ajjeva kiccamātappaṃ,"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "mn132:10.10"
msgid "ko jaññā maraṇaṃ suve;"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "mn132:10.11"
msgid "Na hi no saṅgaraṃ tena,"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "mn132:10.12"
msgid "mahāsenena maccunā."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc17"></a>
msgctxt "mn132:10.13"
msgid "Evaṃvihāriṃ ātāpiṃ,"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "mn132:10.14"
msgid "ahorattamatanditaṃ;"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "mn132:10.15"
msgid "Taṃ ve bhaddekarattoti,"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "mn132:10.16"
msgid "santo ācikkhate munī’ti."
msgstr ""

#. </p></blockquote><p>
#. <a class="nya" id="nya11"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc18"></a>
msgctxt "mn132:11.1"
msgid ""
"Evaṃ kho ahaṃ, bhante, bhikkhūnaṃ dhammiyā kathāya sandassesiṃ samādapesiṃ "
"samuttejesiṃ sampahaṃsesiṃ, bhaddekarattassa uddesañca vibhaṅgañca "
"abhāsin”ti."
msgstr ""
"“That’s how I was inspiring the mendicants with a talk on the recitation "
"passage and analysis of One Fine Night.”"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc19"></a>
msgctxt "mn132:11.2"
msgid "“Sādhu sādhu, ānanda."
msgstr "“Good, good, Ānanda."

msgctxt "mn132:11.3"
msgid ""
"Sādhu kho tvaṃ, ānanda, bhikkhūnaṃ dhammiyā kathāya sandassesi samādapesi "
"samuttejesi sampahaṃsesi, bhaddekarattassa uddesañca vibhaṅgañca abhāsi:"
msgstr ""
"It’s good that you were inspiring the mendicants with a talk on the "
"recitation passage and analysis of One Fine Night.” (And the Buddha repeated "
"the verses and analysis once more.)"

#. </p><blockquote class="gatha"><p>
#. <a class="nya" id="nya12"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc20"></a>
msgctxt "mn132:12.1"
msgid "‘Atītaṃ nānvāgameyya,"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "mn132:12.2"
msgid "… pe …"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "mn132:12.3"
msgid "Taṃ ve bhaddekarattoti,"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "mn132:12.4"
msgid "santo ācikkhate munī’ti."
msgstr ""

#. </p></blockquote><p>
#. <a class="nya" id="nya13-19"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc21"></a>
msgctxt "mn132:13-19.1"
msgid "Kathañca, ānanda, atītaṃ anvāgameti … pe …"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn132:13-19.2"
msgid "evaṃ kho, ānanda, atītaṃ anvāgameti."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn132:13-19.3"
msgid "Kathañca, ānanda, atītaṃ nānvāgameti … pe …"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn132:13-19.4"
msgid "evaṃ kho, ānanda, atītaṃ nānvāgameti."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn132:13-19.5"
msgid "Kathañca, ānanda, anāgataṃ paṭikaṅkhati … pe …"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn132:13-19.6"
msgid "evaṃ kho, ānanda, anāgataṃ paṭikaṅkhati."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn132:13-19.7"
msgid "Kathañca, ānanda, anāgataṃ nappaṭikaṅkhati … pe …"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn132:13-19.8"
msgid "evaṃ kho, ānanda, anāgataṃ nappaṭikaṅkhati."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn132:13-19.9"
msgid "Kathañca, ānanda, paccuppannesu dhammesu saṃhīrati … pe …"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn132:13-19.10"
msgid "evaṃ kho, ānanda, paccuppannesu dhammesu saṃhīrati."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn132:13-19.11"
msgid "Kathañca, ānanda, paccuppannesu dhammesu na saṃhīrati … pe …"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn132:13-19.12"
msgid "evaṃ kho, ānanda, paccuppannesu dhammesu na saṃhīrati."
msgstr ""

#. </p><blockquote class="gatha"><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc22"></a>
msgctxt "mn132:13-19.13"
msgid "‘Atītaṃ nānvāgameyya,"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "mn132:13-19.14"
msgid "… pe …"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "mn132:13-19.15"
msgid "Taṃ ve bhaddekarattoti,"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "mn132:13-19.16"
msgid "santo ācikkhate munī’”ti."
msgstr ""

#. </p></blockquote><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc23"></a>
msgctxt "mn132:13-19.17"
msgid "Idamavoca bhagavā."
msgstr "That is what the Buddha said."

msgctxt "mn132:13-19.18"
msgid "Attamano āyasmā ānando bhagavato bhāsitaṃ abhinandīti."
msgstr "Satisfied, Venerable Ānanda was happy with what the Buddha said."

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "mn132:13-19.19"
msgid "Ānandabhaddekarattasuttaṃ niṭṭhitaṃ dutiyaṃ."
msgstr ""
